---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Experience">
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#64B6FF] to-[#A78BFA] text-transparent bg-clip-text">
    Experience
  </h1>

  <div class="space-y-8">
    <!-- Timeline line -->
    <div class="relative space-y-8">
      <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-0.5 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#64B6FF] to-[#A78BFA] ml-5 md:ml-8"></div>

      <!-- Experience 1 -->
      <div class="relative pl-12 md:pl-16">
        <div class="absolute left-0 w-10 h-10 bg-slate-800 border-2 border-[#64B6FF] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center ml-0.5 md:ml-3.5">
          <img src="/icons/react.svg" alt="React" class="w-6 h-6" />
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg backdrop-blur-sm border border-slate-700/50 transform transition duration-300 hover:scale-[1.02] hover:shadow-xl">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between mb-4">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#64B6FF]">Senior Frontend Developer</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300">Current Company • 2022-Present</p>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-300">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#A78BFA] mt-1 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Led the development of a next-generation web application using Next.js and Tailwind CSS, resulting in a 40% improvement in load times</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#A78BFA] mt-1 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Architected and implemented a reusable component library used across multiple projects, reducing development time by 30%</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#A78BFA] mt-1 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Optimized application performance through code splitting and lazy loading, achieving a 95+ Lighthouse score</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-700/50 rounded-full text-sm text-gray-300">Next.js</span>
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-700/50 rounded-full text-sm text-gray-300">React</span>
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-700/50 rounded-full text-sm text-gray-300">Tailwind CSS</span>
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-700/50 rounded-full text-sm text-gray-300">TypeScript</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Experience 2 -->
      <div class="relative pl-12 md:pl-16">
        <div class="absolute left-0 w-10 h-10 bg-slate-800 border-2 border-[#A78BFA] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center ml-0.5 md:ml-3.5">
          <img src="/icons/node.svg" alt="Node.js" class="w-6 h-6" />
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg backdrop-blur-sm border border-slate-700/50 transform transition duration-300 hover:scale-[1.02] hover:shadow-xl">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between mb-4">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#A78BFA]">Full Stack Developer</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300">Tech Solutions Inc. • 2020-2022</p>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-300">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#64B6FF] mt-1 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Developed and maintained RESTful APIs using Node.js and Express, serving over 1M requests per day</span>
            </li>
